</ol>

<h2>Activate TurboTax Using License Code</h2>

<ol>
<li>Launch the installed <strong>TurboTax Desktop</strong> software.</li>
<li>When prompted, enter your <strong>16-digit TurboTax license code</strong>.</li>
<li>The license code can be found in:
